<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[
  
    Like most murders he is a narcissist who felt he could never get caught. Throughout the book Poirot mentioned on numerous occasions that he understand<a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">…more</a>
    Like most murders he is a narcissist who felt he could never get caught. Throughout the book Poirot mentioned on numerous occasions that he understands psychology. Poirot played on Dr. Shepard's narcissism. <a href="#" rel="nofollow noopener">(less)</a>
  
