<div id="review_2926431073" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2926431073" />
    <a title="Kylie D" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/80033559-kylie-d"><img alt="Kylie D" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1527289322p2/80033559.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2926431073?book_show_action=true">Aug 06, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Kylie D" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Kylie D" href="/user/show/80033559-kylie-d">Kylie D</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780062073563" href="/book/show/9618464-the-murder-of-roger-ackroyd">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/80033559-kylie-d?shelf=annual-challenges">annual-challenges</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/80033559-kylie-d?shelf=monthly-challenges">monthly-challenges</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/80033559-kylie-d?shelf=mystery-crime">mystery-crime</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/80033559-kylie-d?shelf=goodreads-summer-challenge-2019">goodreads-summer-challenge-2019</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2926431073" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17306892201430195749">It&apos;s been many years since this book was released, but it&apos;s still a cut above what&apos;s being published today. Iconic detective Hercule Poirot has retired to the country, but is drawn in to solve a murder. With an ingenious plot, wonderful characters, and an ending that you will never guess, we are again reminded why Agatha Christie is the master at plotting intricate mysteries that all others can only aspire to.</span>
  <span id="freeText17306892201430195749" style="display:none">It's been many years since this book was released, but it's still a cut above what's being published today. Iconic detective Hercule Poirot has retired to the country, but is drawn in to solve a murder. With an ingenious plot, wonderful characters, and an ending that you will never guess, we are again reminded why Agatha Christie is the master at plotting intricate mysteries that all others can only aspire to.</span>
